name: 13th Nice Time
description:
At the top of building, they having a nice time tonight before tomorrow heist. Mowie, Kimchee, and Big Frank enjoy making a blockbuster on billboard while Main City Polize chasing & arrest unknown gang in Route 8O8.

They laughing of it because many gang, especially from Route 8O8, trying to be king in Main City but they never learn how to going big and to the top. Alley Katz believe, everyone who known as a king it was a toy.. from there Mowie, Kimchee, & Big Frank decided to keep on fighting with what they believe & dreaming, the equality for everyone in all universe.

Since the heist is started tomorrow night, they practicing with their all bombing skills in top of 13th floor to be more faster faster faster than ever. Because Alley Katz plan is bombing the propaganda all over the Main City & heisting the Maison de la Banque (Main City big Bank). Of course,  it will cause the MCP (Main City Polize) chasing them for sure.

Be ready for tomorrow night, because it will be a BIG MAYHEM.
